page.title: 07SATURDAY,SLOUGH,1985.
page.content: On Saturdays,I wake up at 8.30 a.m. and have breakfast -branflakes and milk,toast and a cup of tea.I then get washed and dressed. At 10.00 a.m.I go to my friend's house where I play on his computer until lunch. I go home for lunch and in the afternoon I go to Maidenhead for Breakdancing.After this I go home for tea and sometimes go out on my bike. I stay at home in the evening and we normally rent a video film for Saturday, and then I go to bed at 11.00 p.m. which is later than my weektime bedtime at 10.00 p.m. Sundays are very similar, but I spend more time on my B.M.X.bike and do not go "breaking".
